  "body": "<p>Hello everyone! It’s <a href=\"http://ziniaredo.com/\">Zinia</a> here and today I decided to play around with my WeR Memory Keepers Frame punch board and Amy’s latest collection “Sunshine &amp; Good Times” to create a fun mixed media layout.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590559870529-G47UBI6W7UKNOF9KWJKE/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I was looking at my craft supplies and I was really inspired by a color palette from my Distress Oxides. Luckily, those colors were a perfect match with the patterns from Sunshine &amp; Good Times with the addition of some red accents from Hustle &amp; Heart.</p><p>I really love the pastel colors of Sunshine &amp; Good Times but if you add an extra bright color it gets really mindblowing.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590559891118-9FM6ZUD4CQ3OT38L44BW/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>So after I picked patterns that matched the inks I wanted to use, I cut them into squares of various sizes and then turned them into frames using my WeR Memory Keepers frame punch board.</p><p>For the mixed media part I used the inks to created beautiful washes of color around every frame and also to add a few little splatters here and there to fill the empty areas.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590559908638-JDMP92XEPCDKIRT5600L/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I decorated each frame differently but I tried to keep things color coordinating. I used one frame for my photo and one for my journaling. Then I went crazy with the rest playing around with different techniques and ideas.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590559933948-TM61Q1JP4RPNIBY8NBTV/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Since I was playing with inks, it was the perfect opportunity to use the lovely wooden stamps, which are included in the Sunshine &amp; Good Times collection. I used different images for different frames and played around with a few techniques to create interesting effects.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590559951083-VK1UKWV07J60MV87JXVH/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>For my red accents, I pulled a variety of products from previous collections and although there are tiny differences in the warmth of my reds, they all worked beautifully together and complimented the whole design.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590559970208-6E8Z9H0J8SJ5M93X3ARG/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>This is definitely one of the most enjoyable pages I ever created. The process was really fun and I’m madly in love with the whimsical result.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590559988841-S5YDKOGZ06K0FWI03RF8/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>So I really hope you enjoyed this page and you got inspired to create your own unique color palette inspired by your art supplies. Until next time, happy crafting.</p><p>Zinia</p><p><a href=\"http://ziniaredo.com/\">Blog</a> | <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ziniaredo/\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ziniaredo/\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ZiniaRedo/\">Facebook</a></p><p><strong>PRODUCT LIST:</strong></p><p>345688 SUNSHINE &amp; GOOD TIMES 12x12 Paper - Boba Buddy, 345687 SUNSHINE &amp; GOOD TIMES 12x12 Paper - Major Heart Eyes, 345698 SUNSHINE &amp; GOOD TIMES 12x12 Paper - Yesss Please , 345702 SUNSHINE &amp; GOOD TIMES 12x12 Paper - Be Happy, 345713 SUNSHINE &amp; GOOD TIMES - THICKERS Let's Dance, 345712 SUNSHINE &amp; GOOD TIMES - MINI PUFFY STICKERS, 345720 SUNSHINE &amp; GOOD TIMES - STICKER BOOK, 345709 SUNSHINE &amp; GOOD TIMES – EPHEMERA, 345715 SUNSHINE &amp; GOOD TIMES – PAPER CLIPS, 345723 SUNSHINE &amp; GOOD TIMES – WOODEN STAMP INK PAD, 340875 HUSTLE &amp; HEART 12x12 Paper - Hello Sunrise, 341884 HUSTLE &amp; HEART - STICKER BOOK, 341888 HUSTLE &amp; HEART – EPHEMERA, 376223 OH HAPPY LIFE - THICKERS Wild, WeR Memory Keepers Frame Punch Board, Distress Oxide Inks</p><p><em>Thanks for sharing this layout with us, Zinia! Other Design Team member posts can be found </em><a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/?category=amy+tangerine+design+team\"><em>here</em></a><em>. Shop Sunshine and Good Times at your local retailer or online at </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/sunshineandgoodtimes\"><em>Scrapbook.com</em></a></p>"
